1
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:54,930
[A Dream Within A Dream]

2
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:58,009
[Episode 36]

3
00:01:59,150 --> 00:01:59,950
Nan Heng,

4
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:03,790
the script world is governed
by certain rules.

5
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,040
Apart from the two you know,

6
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,120
there are two more.

7
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,280
One is

8
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,259
about how I get back to where I'm from.

9
00:02:10,259 --> 00:02:11,590
As long as Song Yimeng and you

10
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:12,870
finish all the iconic scenes

11
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:13,870
till the finale,

12
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:15,280
I'll be brought back to the modern times.

13
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,760
The other one is,

14
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,940
changes of iconic scenes will backfire

15
00:02:21,940 --> 00:02:23,400
on those who induce them.

16
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:27,180
[Trouble finds those
who change the iconic scenes]

17
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,970
Backfire?

18
00:02:31,450 --> 00:02:32,640
Then Song Yimeng...

19
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,590
She'll be fine.

20
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:34,770
Think about it.

21
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,070
What has she changed?

22
00:02:36,870 --> 00:02:38,079
She did fall into the water
in the royal garden

23
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:39,070
as the script says.

24
00:02:39,070 --> 00:02:40,400
She was rescued by a hero
at the Lantern Festival

25
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,280
as the script says.

26
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,630
She did defy the Song family

27
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:43,650
as the script says.

28
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:46,030
She even caught you
in bed with Song Yiting

29
00:02:46,030 --> 00:02:47,590
as the script says.

30
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:49,130
The only change happened

31
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,430
on the wedding day,

32
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:52,079
when you used the script rules

33
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:53,630
to break the script rules.

34
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:55,400
So, Nan Heng,

35
00:02:56,290 --> 00:02:57,950
in the script world,

36
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,060
you're the only one character

37
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,470
who can change the iconic scenes.

38
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:09,150
That's good.

39
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:09,750
Good?

40
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,560
If the upcoming plots go

41
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,150
further and further
into the opposite direction--

42
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:17,800
for example, Song Yiting
marries Shangguan He--

43
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:20,200
then you,
who induced the initial changes,

44
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,010
will be hurt even worse,

45
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,710
till you die.

46
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:24,870
Understood?

47
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:29,030
So this is why you helped
to forge a marital union

48
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,760
between Song Yiting and Shangguan He?

49
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,520
Hold on.

50
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,520
What did he tell you?

51
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,610
My uncle said,

52
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:38,290
based on his years of study on storybooks,

53
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:40,050
only an external force was needed to

54
00:03:40,050 --> 00:03:42,000
compel Shangguan He
to express his love for Yiting,

55
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,840
and that I was

56
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,520
this force.

57
00:03:47,690 --> 00:03:49,690
I didn't mean to be this cruel to you,

58
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:52,260
but Song Yimeng stubbornly

59
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:54,350
refused to play along with the plots.

60
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:56,240
Nan Heng,

61
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,430
take my advice.

62
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,960
If you want to stay alive,

63
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,280
then just abide by

64
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,940
the rules of the script world.

65
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,380
If I had ever played by the book,

66
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,020
how could you have been brought here?

67
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,510
Still acting tough, aren't you?

68
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:18,610
To be honest,

69
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,680
if you still try to change the story,

70
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:21,920
you will die

71
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,180
in less than a month.

72
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,410
When that happens,

73
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,800
how do you think I will hurt Song Yimeng?

74
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:31,120
Or maybe I should just wait

75
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:33,780
till you die, huh?

76
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:49,470
Chu Guihong.

77
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,050
Do you know who you are protecting?

78
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:56,790
Someone who can help me
return to the capital.

79
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,310
It's my father, of course.

80
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,580
Would your father ever

81
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,430
behave like this?

82
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:03,870
Open your eyes and look...

83
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:04,600
Nan Heng,

84
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:08,260
people would only believe
what's in their best interests.

85
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,950
I'm no exception.

86
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,500
This is what you taught me.

87
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,240
Those who are seen as villains

88
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,680
will be praised for doing

89
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,070
just one good deed.

90
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,630
Now, Miss Song Yiting

91
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:25,430
and Shangguan He are engaged.

92
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:27,880
It was my father who helped to make

93
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:28,890
this beautiful thing happen.

94
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:29,690
And you...

95
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:34,720
You're just a loser who's slowly dying.

96
00:05:41,659 --> 00:05:42,540
Dad,

97
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,570
the wind is rising.

98
00:05:48,050 --> 00:05:49,400
Let's go.

99
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,720
You...

100
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:50,030
I already had Rong Hua
figure out the truth.

101
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,400
At Pingrong Battle,

102
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,950
my father was indeed killed
by Heyuan people.

103
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,550
He had no chance of survival.

104
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,830
Confess now.

105
00:06:58,580 --> 00:07:00,070
Who really are you?

106
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:01,630
What does "character" mean?

107
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,870
What is "the script world"?

108
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:03,510
Also,

109
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:05,750
who am I?

110
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,070
Jixiang,

111
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,800
did you see?

112
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:17,430
Even Uncle couldn't formally conclude
the long overdue engagement

113
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,240
between Yiting and He.

114
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,430
But I had it done

115
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:21,630
at my first attempt.

116
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,830
I really am Cupid in human form.

117
00:07:26,310 --> 00:07:28,000
Your Highness, you don't have to talk

118
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,270
when you feel upset.

119
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,160
What's the matter with you?

120
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,000
Y-Y-You...

121
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,430
D-Don't call out my lie.

122
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,480
Your Highness!

123
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:38,040
Yiting?

124
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,810
Why are you out here?

125
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,510
Why did you help me

126
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,740
in the Waning River Crescent's Hall?

127
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:56,750
Yiting,

128
00:07:57,560 --> 00:08:00,070
though it was Uncle's request
for help that brought me here,

129
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,710
I did mean to do you a favor.

130
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:09,440
Actually, during these days,

131
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,480
I've done a lot of thinking.

132
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:14,440
It's time I stopped pestering you,

133
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,000
since you're way out of my league.

134
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,970
What do you mean?

135
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,180
Yiting,

136
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,120
no other girls in the capital...

137
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,920
No.

138
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,789
No other girls in Great Jing
are better than you.

139
00:08:32,789 --> 00:08:34,549
You have your own insights on everything.

140
00:08:34,549 --> 00:08:36,870
You dare to go against conventions.

141
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,510
But what about me?

142
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,500
I'm just a silly boy

143
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,100
who has no opinions of his own

144
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,580
and hides behind his father all the time.

145
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:46,840
I'm neither knowledgeable,

146
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,840
nor astute

147
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,960
in politics.

148
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,250
I'm not good enough for you.

149
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,270
After thinking that through,

150
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:54,730
I actually felt relieved.

151
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:59,870
Now, I wish you and Shangguan He

152
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,510
a happy marriage.

153
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:04,440
Thanks for your blessings.

154
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,040
But, Your Highness,

155
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:08,270
you shouldn't sell yourself short.

156
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:11,040
Academic and political achievements

157
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:13,150
aren't enough to define a man.

158
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:16,510
Similarly, a woman shouldn't be judged

159
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,910
by her temperament
and marriage status.

160
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,960
Your Highness
was born into the royal family,

161
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,330
yet you're pure of heart

162
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:24,320
and kind.

163
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:27,360
Not everyone can be like you.

164
00:09:27,770 --> 00:09:28,700
You are cheerful

165
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,700
and outspoken.

166
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:32,110
These traits are as valuable

167
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:34,010
and priceless as academic

168
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,780
and political achievements.

169
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:37,680
So, I believe Your Highness

170
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,320
will find a girl you love,

171
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,030
who truly loves you back.

172
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,150
Thanks.

173
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:46,480
Yiting.

174
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:48,670
Wait.

175
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:51,480
Did you say that because I'm stupid?

176
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,870
Your Highness is not stupid at all.

177
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,470
You're a man of great wisdom.

178
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,840
You reflect on yourself
without others' reminders.

179
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,570
You're tolerant and generous.

180
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,810
You dropped a grudge
that lasted for ten-odd years,

181
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:06,260
and peacefully accepted

182
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,720
that your brother became the crown prince.

183
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:11,240
You also kindly helped a girl
fight for her true love,

184
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:13,240
though she had rejected you before.

185
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,300
Not everyone

186
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:18,150
is capable of doing these.

187
00:10:25,020 --> 00:10:25,830
Right.

188
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,370
I always know it.

189
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:30,750
I’m still the remarkable chosen one,

190
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,620
who symbolizes good fortune.

191
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,080
Well, Yiting,

192
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,030
will you

193
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:44,030
be friends with me,
the man standing for

194
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,160
auspiciousness?

195
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,450
It'll be my honor to be friends

196
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,610
with Your Highness.

197
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,920
That's great.

198
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,290
I've told you the gist.

199
00:10:58,510 --> 00:11:00,100
In the script world,

200
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,840
Nan Heng is the male lead.

201
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:04,720
He will kill his brother
and ascend the throne at last.

202
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,520
As for you, the cannon fodder...

203
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:10,120
I mean the second male lead.

204
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,880
You will be killed by Nan Heng

205
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,000
and completely vanish

206
00:11:14,030 --> 00:11:16,480
after he becomes the Emperor.

207
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,840
He has done tons of evil,

208
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,270
including causing my father's death

209
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,930
and stealing my fiancée away.

210
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:40,620
He'll even tread me under foot in the end?

211
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,270
Why?

212
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,320
Because he's the male lead.

213
00:11:48,220 --> 00:11:49,280
Then what about me?

214
00:11:49,730 --> 00:11:51,420
Why can't I be the protagonist?

215
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,390
How am I inferior to him?

216
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:53,630
Y-Y-You...

217
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:55,050
You're not inferior to him.

218
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:57,290
W-W-Well...

219
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:58,720
How about...

220
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,670
How about this?

221
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,150
If you play along

222
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:05,550
with the plot of choosing
one out of the two hostages,

223
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:07,480
I'll change the ending

224
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:09,850
w-when I'm back to the modern times.

225
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:11,670
I'll make you the male lead!

226
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,260
As it turns out,

227
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,720
you'd like to make a deal with me.

228
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,810
Do you know

229
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,360
what I want now?

230
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:34,840
Of course I do.

231
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:37,440
You want to kill Nan Heng

232
00:12:37,670 --> 00:12:40,670
and help your cousin Nan Rui
ascend the throne, right?

233
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,200
I do want Nan Heng dead.

234
00:12:48,540 --> 00:12:50,600
But I also want to hold my fate

235
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:52,410
in my own hands.

236
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,360
In this vast world,

237
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:00,410
nobody can constrain me anymore.

238
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,640
You want to ascend the throne yourself?

239
00:13:16,250 --> 00:13:17,310
What are you doing?

240
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:19,680
You...

241
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:21,730
Don't do anything stupid.

242
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,160
What exactly are you going to do?

243
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:33,240
If you are to make a deal with me,

244
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:36,140
meet me in two hours

245
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:38,240
in Qianyu Mansion.

246
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,440
How am I supposed

247
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,500
to go back this way?

248
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,390
You're sick!

249
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:48,630
You make me sick!

250
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,840
I didn't

251
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:53,040
portray him as a crazy guy in the script.

252
00:13:56,190 --> 00:13:57,950
[Iconic Scenes in the Script]

253
00:13:58,020 --> 00:14:01,350
[No. 6: The classic--
choosing to save one
out of the two hostages on the city tower]

254
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:05,610
Heng suffered a lot
in the cold palace when he was little.

255
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:08,440
He then spent years
on the dangerous battlefield.

256
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:16,990
[Moral Cultivation]

257
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,930
Now, he has finally
come back alive from the borders.

258
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,840
His life has just become safer and better.

259
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:17,370
How did this misfortune
suddenly befall him?

260
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,950
I've ordered an investigation.

261
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,200
Song Yude said,

262
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:29,630
when the servants in the Song Residence
discovered Heng,

263
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,000
he had sunk into a coma.

264
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,550
Nobody was around him.

265
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,530
Your Majesty.

266
00:14:35,530 --> 00:14:36,390
Your Ladyship.

267
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:38,030
Your Majesty.

268
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:38,890
Your Ladyship.

269
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:41,420
The royal physicians have rushed
to the crown prince's residence.

270
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:43,630
They said His Highness
had a medical emergency.

271
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,910
Physician Qin is performing
acupuncture on His Highness now.

272
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:47,670
There will be results soon.

273
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:50,670
Yes.

274
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,760
Don't worry.

275
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,200
Heng is a blessed child.

276
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,000
He'll surely get better.

277
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:06,840
His unfortunate life is attributed to me,

278
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:10,440
his useless mother.

279
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:13,860
The biggest regret of my life

280
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:16,740
is not being a good enough mother to Heng.

281
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,840
It is I

282
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:20,930
who owe him a lot,

283
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:23,630
not you.

284
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:45,600
