320
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:12,190
Are you lying to me or not?

321
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,240
I'm not.

322
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:16,960
Well,

323
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:19,240
I'd better ask Physician Qin about it.

324
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:20,300
Come back!

325
