326
00:17:21,589 --> 00:17:22,829
This is a secret.

327
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,400
Letting it out won't do

328
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,450
any good.

329
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,750
Besides, think about this.

330
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,270
