333
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,890
for refusing to cooperate

334
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:33,830
and

335
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,240
to go through the plots.

336
00:17:42,510 --> 00:17:44,400
Is that all?

