I'm not a wise ruler,

587
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:54,550
but at least I should be a good father.

588
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,930
As long as you are healthy and safe,

589
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,200
I won't

590
