feel ashamed when I meet your mother again

591
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:04,030
in heaven.

592
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:04,830
Father,

593
00:30:04,850 --> 00:30:06,030
where-

594
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:08,090
