and even depressed.

600
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:16,680
Father,

601
00:30:17,670 --> 00:30:18,730
I've actually

602
00:30:18,750 --> 00:30:21,590
asked the Imperial Astronomical Bureau
in private.

603
00:30:21,590 --> 00:30:22,790
Heng fell ill

604
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:24,440
probably because he was invaded

605
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,720
by something evil.

606
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:28,920
To cure him,

607
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:31,750
we must use the righteousness
deep within our souls

608
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:33,000
and heartfelt joy

609
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,220
to suppress the evil.

610
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,680
I was going to suggest you

611
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,960
