Father, why are you ignoring me?

621
00:30:58,460 --> 00:30:59,720
Did I say anything wrong?

622
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,520
It's not that.

623
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,520
I'm just eating this tangerine.

624
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:03,310
It's so delicious.

625
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,000
Okay then.

626
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,790
Very tasty.

627
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:05,560
That's good.

628
00:31:06,070 --> 00:31:06,720
Father,

629
00:31:07,110 --> 00:31:07,920
will you issue

630
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,400
an imperial edict

631
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:11,330
to draw that evil thing out of Heng?

632
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:15,280
Father, are you alright?

633
