637
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:32,920
Father.

638
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:33,790
Father!

639
00:31:33,810 --> 00:31:34,880
Father!

640
00:31:34,900 --> 00:31:35,650
Father!

641
