I'm worried.

642
00:31:36,590 --> 00:31:37,680
Father!

643
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:39,790
Royal physicians!

644
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:41,070
Your Majesty!

645
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:41,400
What's wrong?

646
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,630
I'm frightened!

647
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:43,920
Guards!

648
00:31:43,940 --> 00:31:45,920
The Eighteenth Prince
poisoned the Emperor!

649
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:47,030
Help!

650
00:31:47,050 --> 00:31:49,240
The Eighteenth Prince
poisoned the Emperor!

651
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,310
Help!

652
00:31:50,310 --> 00:31:51,030
No.

653
00:31:51,270 --> 00:31:52,070
No.

654
00:31:52,090 --> 00:31:53,310
I didn't.

655
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:54,390
Father...

656
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,540
Run...

657
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:57,220
Ask Heng for help...

658
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:06,540
Your Highness.

659
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,410
Jixiang, Jixiang!

660
00:32:08,430 --> 00:32:09,830
People are chasing after me.

661
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:11,000
They said I poisoned Father,

662
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:11,880
but I didn't.

663
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,270
I really didn't!

664
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,000
I know.

665
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:14,440
Let's go

666
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,310
find the crown prince.

667
00:32:15,310 --> 00:32:15,750
Okay.

668
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:25,880
Guihong,

669
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:27,030
