670
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:28,720
Father somehow got poisoned.

671
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,250
Come with me to check it out.

672
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:34,110
Qianyu Army is ordered
to defend the sovereign

673
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:36,510
and seize the culprit
who poisoned the Emperor.

674
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,310
Take him down!

675
00:32:37,760 --> 00:32:39,190
Back off!

676
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:42,520
Nan Rui, you're the culprit.

677
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,420
Are you defying the order?

678
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:45,240
I...

679
