He did nothing wrong.

680
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:47,550
He's not the culprit.

681
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:49,080
How is he defying the order?

682
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:50,730
What a stubborn offender.

683
00:32:52,510 --> 00:32:53,480
Qianyu Army

684
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:55,510
will still carry out its duties.

685
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:56,910
When swords are wielded,

686
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,090
there may be

687
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,640
bloodshed.

688
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,070
Strike!

689
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,680
Jixiang...

690
00:33:25,790 --> 00:33:26,860
Jixiang.

691
00:33:27,070 --> 00:33:28,190
Jixiang.

692
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:29,240
Jixiang.

693
00:33:30,020 --> 00:33:31,730
Don't trust Chu Guihong.

694
00:33:32,270 --> 00:33:33,340
Your Highness,

695
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:35,140
go find the crown prince now.

696
00:33:35,170 --> 00:33:36,240
I know.

697
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,000
I know.

698
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,000
Stop talking.

699
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,320
Where are the royal physicians?

700
00:33:39,320 --> 00:33:40,260
Royal physicians...

701
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:41,480
Where are the royal physicians?

702
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,040
Get me a royal physician!

703
00:33:43,170 --> 00:33:43,980
Jixiang.

704
00:33:44,010 --> 00:33:44,850
Jixiang!

705
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:46,110
Let go of me!

706
00:33:46,830 --> 00:33:47,640
Jixiang!

707
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:48,550
Jixiang!

708
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:49,690
Please don't die,

709
00:33:49,710 --> 00:33:50,560
Jixiang!

710
00:33:50,590 --> 00:33:52,160
I've lost everything.

711
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,890
You're all I have now, Jixiang!

712
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:55,620
Jixiang!

713
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,820
Let go of me!

714
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:01,030
Jixiang!

715
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:11,920
Guihong...

716
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:13,480
Why?

717
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:14,880
Why?

718
00:34:15,010 --> 00:34:17,340
Why are you doing this to me?

719
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:25,380
Do you have something to do
with Father being poisoned?

720
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,960
Answer me.

721
00:34:27,590 --> 00:34:29,389
Answer me now!

722
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:31,550
Give me an answer!

723
00:34:42,620 --> 00:34:44,000
Xuanjia Army is here executing

724
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,710
the crown prince's order
to take the Eighteenth Prince away!

725
00:34:46,710 --> 00:34:47,719
General Chu,

726
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:49,210
free the prince now.

727
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,880
Release him.

728
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:10,780
Your Highness,

729
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,590
what should we do

730
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:13,990
in this critical moment?

731
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,880
I beg for your instructions.

732
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:19,880
The Ministry of Justice has interrogated
the red tangerine vendor.

733
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:21,840
The eunuchs guarding outside
the Emperor's bed chamber and Liu Mingxi

734
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:23,170
have all given their statements.

735
00:35:23,170 --> 00:35:24,570
It is proven
that the Eighteenth Prince

736
00:35:24,570 --> 00:35:27,300
personally fed
those tangerines to the Emperor.

737
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,190
This...

738
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:30,030
This is solid evidence.

739
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:36,780
Your Highness.

740
00:35:38,830 --> 00:35:40,360
What's the situation like?

741
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:42,550
Your Highness,

742
00:35:42,550 --> 00:35:44,510
the royal physicians
have carefully examined

743
00:35:44,510 --> 00:35:47,000
the poison found
in the Eighteenth Prince's residence

744
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:48,320
by Qianyu Army.

745
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:51,670
It is identical to the poison
in the red tangerines.

746
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:53,670
I'm asking about the Emperor!

747
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:57,510
His Majesty is unconscious

748
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,110
with shallow breaths now.

749
00:35:59,140 --> 00:36:00,280
According to Physician Qin,

750
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:02,030
this poison is highly toxic.

751
00:36:02,030 --> 00:36:02,890
It is likely...

752
00:36:03,110 --> 00:36:05,570
It is likely to endanger
His Majesty's life!

753
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:08,750
Go tell Physician Qin

754
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,690
to save the Emperor's life

755
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,050
with whatever potent drugs

756
00:36:12,050 --> 00:36:13,510
or by any means necessary.

757
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:14,710
I'll bear all the consequences

758
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:15,900
that may lead to.

759
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:17,650
Yes.

760
00:36:20,030 --> 00:36:21,070
Here comes the crown prince.

761
00:36:21,070 --> 00:36:22,590
Your Highness.

762
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:23,760
Your Highness!

763
00:36:26,110 --> 00:36:26,970
Your Highness,

764
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:29,190
there are witnesses
and physical evidence.

765
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:31,480
The Eighteenth Prince Nan Rui is a rebel
who attempted to murder the Emperor.

766
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:33,230
This is an unpardonable offense.

767
00:36:33,230 --> 00:36:34,550
Your Highness must punish him severely.

768
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:35,320
Yes.

769
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,840
The court is in turmoil now.

770
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,300
Danger is lurking around.

771
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:40,920
Your Highness must
take decisive measures now,

772
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,670
or the court will be mortally disturbed

773
00:36:42,670 --> 00:36:43,230
and the country deeply shaken...

774
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:43,800
Shut up!

775
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:54,030
Nan Rui is my brother.

776
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:55,630
No one knows him

777
00:36:55,630 --> 00:36:57,000
better than I do.

778
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:00,590
No matter who asks me,

779
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:03,000
be it an official, a citizen,

780
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:04,670
or anyone else,

781
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:06,130
I'll give the same answer.

782
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,590
That is, Nan Rui can't be the culprit.

783
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:09,440
Do you hear me?

784
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:11,820
Your Highness,

785
00:37:12,190 --> 00:37:13,990
should the Ministry of Justice

786
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:16,230
investigate this case or not?

787
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:17,550
Keep investigating it,

788
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:19,080
till the truth is revealed.

789
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:19,960
Yes.

790
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:25,360
What are the odds?

791
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:28,240
Shortly after Nan Heng fell ill,

792
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,740
the Emperor was poisoned.

793
00:37:31,150 --> 00:37:33,230
How could it have been done by Nan Rui?

794
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:38,780
Your Highness!

795
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:44,710
The royal kitchen
has sent you food three times.

796
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:46,440
Please eat something.

797
00:37:46,590 --> 00:37:48,190
No, I don't have an appetite.

798
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,140
There must be hidden secrets.

799
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,770
Even so,

800
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:55,070
you can't proceed with the case

801
00:37:55,070 --> 00:37:56,760
with an empty stomach.

802
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,290
Word from the royal medical office

803
00:37:59,290 --> 00:38:02,130
says the Emperor might die tonight.

804
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,670
When the crown prince ascends the throne,

805
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:05,280
there will be many issues

806
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:07,010
for Your Highness to attend to.

807
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:08,530
Ascend the throne?

808
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:10,760
How could I forget about this?

809
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:12,960
By the time the hostage situation happens,

810
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:14,960
Nan Heng has become the new emperor.

811
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:15,920
Nan Heng!

812
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:21,980
[A Dream of Qingning]
[Scene 19, Episode 37]

813
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:17,230
You don't deserve the throne

814
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:18,000
for persecuting faithful officials

815
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,360
and committing regicide and patricide!

816
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:21,440
If you want to save these women,

817
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:23,770
then take your own life right here!

818
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:26,110
How dare you threaten me?

819
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,670
Zhixia,

820
00:38:30,690 --> 00:38:31,840
where is Shangguan He?

821
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:34,030
He has gone to the Song Residence
to pick up Miss Yiting.

822
00:38:34,030 --> 00:38:35,230
Have someone deliver him a message.

823
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:36,480
Tell him to protect Yiting

824
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,400
and to stay close to her.

825
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,280
Do you get it?

826
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,110
Go do it now!

827
00:38:39,110 --> 00:38:39,800
Yes.

828
00:38:43,150 --> 00:38:43,960
Yingqiu,

829
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,760
go borrow a Xuanjia troop for me.

830
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:47,070
