844
00:40:25,230 --> 00:40:26,800
It is you who caused

845
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,440
this dire situation.

846
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,630
Who are you showing

847
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:33,070
